{
  "info": {
    "name": "Finanzas Mayeson - Chequeo IA / 502",
    "description": "Coleccion independiente para diagnosticar el 502 de SyntheroLink y confirmar que el Worker responde con fallback.\n\nPasos:\n1. Llena las variables de la coleccion (Variables): provider_url, provider_key, login_password, y chat_id si quieres forzar usuario.\n2. Ejecuta '1. Proveedor directo (502 check)' -> dice si SyntheroLink ya volvio.\n3. Ejecuta '2. Login' -> guarda auth_token solo.\n4. Ejecuta '3. Advisor (Worker)' -> confirma source ai/local.\n\nLos resultados clave se imprimen en la Postman Console (View > Show Postman Console).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://finanzas-d1-api.mayersonm.workers.dev" },
    { "key": "provider_url", "value": "https://api.synterolink.com/v1/messages" },
    { "key": "provider_chat_url", "value": "https://api.synterolink.com/v1/chat/completions" },
    { "key": "provider_key", "value": "" },
    { "key": "provider_model", "value": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001" },
    { "key": "login_email", "value": "mayersonm@gmail.com" },
    { "key": "login_password", "value": "" },
    { "key": "challenge_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "otp_code", "value": "" },
    { "key": "auth_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "chat_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Health del Worker",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": "{{base_url}}/health",
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "console.log('Health status:', pm.response.code, pm.response.text());",
              "pm.test('Worker vivo (200 ok)', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Proveedor directo (502 check)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{provider_key}}" },
          { "key": "anthropic-version", "value": "2023-06-01" }
        ],
        "url": "{{provider_url}}",
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"model\": \"{{provider_model}}\",\n  \"max_tokens\": 64,\n  \"messages\": [{ \"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Responde solo: ok\" }]\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "description": "Llama DIRECTO a SyntheroLink (sin pasar por tu Worker). Si tu proveedor usa Authorization: Bearer en vez de x-api-key, cambia el header. Asi sabes si el 502 ya paso."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const code = pm.response.code;",
              "console.log('SyntheroLink status:', code);",
              "if (code === 200) {",
              "  console.log('OK -> el proveedor ya responde. Tu chat IA volvera a \"IA activa\" solo.');",
              "} else if (code === 502 || code === 503 || code === 504) {",
              "  console.log('Gateway caido (' + code + ') -> sigue el problema del proveedor. Solo esperar.');",
              "} else if (code === 403) {",
              "  console.log('403 -> no es caida: revisa el grupo/permiso de tu key para /v1/messages.');",
              "} else if (code === 401) {",
              "  console.log('401 -> key invalida o header equivocado (x-api-key vs Authorization Bearer).');",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('Respuesta:', pm.response.text().slice(0, 300));",
              "}",
              "pm.test('Proveedor responde 200', () => pm.expect(code).to.eql(200));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1b. Proveedor /chat/completions (test salida)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{provider_key}}" }
        ],
        "url": "{{provider_chat_url}}",
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"model\": \"{{provider_model}}\",\n  \"max_tokens\": 64,\n  \"messages\": [\n    { \"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"Responde en una linea.\" },\n    { \"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Responde solo: ok\" }\n  ]\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "description": "Misma key pero por /v1/chat/completions (formato OpenAI, header Authorization Bearer). Si AQUI viene el texto en choices[].message.content, se puede arreglar por codigo. Si tambien viene vacio, hay que cambiar el grupo de la key o usar Anthropic directo."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const code = pm.response.code;",
              "let data = {};",
              "try { data = pm.response.json(); } catch (e) {}",
              "const text = data.choices && data.choices[0] && data.choices[0].message && data.choices[0].message.content;",
              "console.log('chat/completions status:', code, '| texto:', text ? JSON.stringify(text) : '(vacio)');",
              "if (text) {",
              "  console.log('SI hay texto por chat/completions -> se puede arreglar por codigo (fallback ante content vacio).');",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('Tambien vacio -> cambia el grupo de la key en SyntheroLink o usa Anthropic directo.');",
              "}",
              "pm.test('chat/completions trae texto', () => pm.expect(Boolean(text)).to.eql(true));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1c. Formato foto (content array, sin system)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{provider_key}}" },
          { "key": "anthropic-version", "value": "2023-06-01" }
        ],
        "url": "{{provider_url}}",
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"model\": \"{{provider_model}}\",\n  \"max_tokens\": 300,\n  \"messages\": [{\n    \"role\": \"user\",\n    \"content\": [\n      { \"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"Responde SOLO con este JSON: {\\\"ok\\\": true}\" }\n    ]\n  }]\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "description": "Replica el formato EXACTO del analisis de foto (content como array de bloques, sin parametro system top-level), pero solo texto. Si AQUI viene content con texto, la solucion es cambiar el formato del chat al de la foto (arreglable por codigo)."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const code = pm.response.code;",
              "let data = {};",
              "try { data = pm.response.json(); } catch (e) {}",
              "const block = (data.content || []).find(b => b && b.type === 'text');",
              "const text = block && block.text;",
              "console.log('formato-foto status:', code, '| content.length:', (data.content || []).length, '| texto:', text ? JSON.stringify(text) : '(vacio)');",
              "if (text) {",
              "  console.log('FUNCIONA con formato array -> arreglo el chat por codigo replicando el formato de la foto.');",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('Tambien vacio -> el grupo nunca devuelve texto; toca cambiar grupo/Anthropic directo.');",
              "}",
              "pm.test('content trae texto', () => pm.expect(Boolean(text)).to.eql(true));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1d. Formato recibo (imagen 1x1 + texto)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{provider_key}}" },
          { "key": "anthropic-version", "value": "2023-06-01" }
        ],
        "url": "{{provider_url}}",
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"model\": \"{{provider_model}}\",\n  \"max_tokens\": 64,\n  \"messages\": [{\n    \"role\": \"user\",\n    \"content\": [\n      { \"type\": \"image\", \"source\": { \"type\": \"base64\", \"media_type\": \"image/png\", \"data\": \"iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVR42mNkYPhfDwAChwGA60e6kgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" } },\n      { \"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"Ignora la imagen (esta vacia). Responde SOLO con este JSON: {\\\"ok\\\": true}\" }\n    ]\n  }]\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "description": "Replica el modo multimodal del recibo: una imagen 1x1 transparente + texto. Si AQUI viene content con texto, confirmamos que el truco funciona y lo aplico al chat (imagen invisible para forzar el modo que si responde)."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const code = pm.response.code;",
              "let data = {};",
              "try { data = pm.response.json(); } catch (e) {}",
              "const block = (data.content || []).find(b => b && b.type === 'text');",
              "const text = block && block.text;",
              "console.log('imagen+texto status:', code, '| content.length:', (data.content || []).length, '| texto:', text ? JSON.stringify(text) : '(vacio)');",
              "if (text) {",
              "  console.log('FUNCIONA -> aplico el truco de imagen invisible al chat IA por codigo.');",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('Vacio incluso con imagen -> ni el modo recibo da texto; toca cambiar grupo/Anthropic.');",
              "}",
              "pm.test('content trae texto con imagen', () => pm.expect(Boolean(text)).to.eql(true));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1e. Streaming (como el SDK / OpenCode)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{provider_key}}" },
          { "key": "anthropic-version", "value": "2023-06-01" }
        ],
        "url": "{{provider_url}}",
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"model\": \"{{provider_model}}\",\n  \"max_tokens\": 64,\n  \"stream\": true,\n  \"messages\": [{ \"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Responde solo: ok\" }]\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "description": "Llama con stream:true, como hace el SDK de Anthropic (OpenCode). La respuesta es SSE (eventos). Si aqui aparece el texto en content_block_delta/text_delta, entonces SyntheroLink solo entrega por streaming y ahi esta la solucion."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const raw = pm.response.text();",
              "console.log('streaming status:', pm.response.code);",
              "console.log('crudo (primeros 800):', raw.slice(0, 800));",
              "const hasText = /text_delta|content_block_delta/.test(raw);",
              "if (hasText) {",
              "  console.log('HAY texto en el stream -> SyntheroLink entrega por STREAMING. La solucion es usar stream:true.');",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('Sin texto en el stream tampoco -> el grupo de la key no entrega texto por ningun modo.');",
              "}",
              "pm.test('El stream trae deltas de texto', () => pm.expect(hasText).to.eql(true));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Login (Worker)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/login",
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{login_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{login_password}}\"\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "description": "Inicia sesion. Si tienes 2FA activo, devuelve requires2fa + challengeToken: usa entonces '2b. Login 2FA'."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const data = pm.response.json();",
              "if (data.requires2fa && data.challengeToken) {",
              "  pm.collectionVariables.set('challenge_token', data.challengeToken);",
              "  console.log('2FA requerido -> pon tu codigo en la variable otp_code y ejecuta \"2b. Login 2FA\".');",
              "} else if (data.token) {",
              "  pm.collectionVariables.set('auth_token', data.token);",
              "  console.log('Login OK -> auth_token guardado.');",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('Login fallo:', pm.response.code, pm.response.text().slice(0, 200));",
              "}",
              "pm.test('Login respondio 200', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2b. Login 2FA (si aplica)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/login/2fa",
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"challengeToken\": \"{{challenge_token}}\",\n  \"code\": \"{{otp_code}}\"\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "description": "Solo si '2. Login' pidio 2FA. Pon tu codigo de 6 digitos en la variable otp_code antes de ejecutar."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const data = pm.response.json();",
              "if (data.token) {",
              "  pm.collectionVariables.set('auth_token', data.token);",
              "  console.log('2FA OK -> auth_token guardado.');",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('2FA fallo:', pm.response.code, pm.response.text().slice(0, 200));",
              "}",
              "pm.test('2FA respondio 200', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Advisor (Worker)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "url": "{{base_url}}/api/ai/advisor?chat_id={{chat_id}}",
        "auth": {
          "type": "bearer",
          "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"mode\": \"chat\",\n  \"question\": \"cuanto puedo gastar hoy?\"\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "description": "Pega por tu Worker. Confirma que el dashboard responde aunque SyntheroLink este caido (source: local)."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const data = pm.response.json();",
              "console.log('source:', data.source, '| providerStatus:', data.providerStatus, '| title:', data.title);",
              "if (data.source === 'ai') {",
              "  console.log('IA activa -> el proveedor respondio bien.');",
              "} else if (data.source === 'local') {",
              "  console.log('Modo local -> tu API responde con analisis local; el proveedor sigue caido.');",
              "}",
              "pm.test('Advisor respondio 200', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200));",
              "pm.test('Trae un consejo', () => pm.expect(data).to.have.property('ok', true));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
